prompt v0.0.2

Ingmar Land and Robby McKilliam 6/2/2012

A beamer addon for presentations allowing you to inform your audience of the response you desire them to express.  Simple usage:

\usepackage{prompt}

\silence : Usher silence from your audience
\attention : Command the attention of your audience
\surprise : Indicate that a flabbergasting result has been displayed
\laughter : Prompt your audience regarding a hilarious gag
\applause : Demand recognition at the end of your glorious presentation

See example.tex for an example of the intended use of prompt.
 
